  "title": "Food Crew",
  "description": "<h2><strong>✨ Kimhodu Food Crew ✨</strong></h2><p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Food Crew / Bakery Assistant (Full-Time / Part-Time)</p><h3><strong>Company Overview</strong></h3><p>Kimhodu is a popular bakery brand from Korea, specialising in freshly baked walnut puff cakes and warm customer service. We are looking for friendly, responsible, and motivated individuals to join our growing team.</p><h3><strong>📍 Work Location</strong></h3><p>Blk 539 Bedok North Street 3<br />#01-653, Singapore 460539</p><h3><strong>🕒 Working Hours</strong></h3><p>• 7:30 AM – 5:30 PM<br />• Full-Time / Part-Time positions available<br />• Flexible shift arrangements</p><h3><strong>💼 Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><p>• Prepare and bake walnut puff cakes according to company standards<br />• Maintain store cleanliness and hygiene<br />• Operate cashier and assist customers<br />• Support daily store operations and perform other assigned duties</p><h3><strong>✅ Job Requirements</strong></h3><p>• Friendly, responsible, and positive attitude<br />• Willing to learn and work well in a team<br />• No prior experience required (training provided)<br />• Able to work flexible shifts and rotate between outlets if required</p><h3><strong>🎁 Benefits</strong></h3><p>• On-the-job training provided<br />• Commission and incentive schemes<br />• Friendly and supportive working environment</p><h3><strong>💰 Salary & Work Schedule</strong></h3><p><strong>Full-Time:</strong><br />• <strong>5-Day Work Week</strong> (1 weekday + 1 weekend day off):<br />  $2,000 + $150 Work Incentive<br />• <strong>6-Day Work Week</strong> (Choose 1 day off):<br />  $2,200 + $150 Work Incentive</p><p><strong>Part-Time:</strong><br />• Regular Days (Mon–Sun): $10/hour<br />• Public Holidays (e.g. National Day): $12/hour</p><h3><strong>📩 How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume/CV to:<br />📧 <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hr@uonegolive.com</a></p>",
